721547f-b.title: Manhattan: Madison Street - Gouverneur Street
721547f-b.text:
(1)
Nadis n Street, northside looking eastward from Couverneur Street, Williensburg 3ridge ray be seen in hackgro nd.
(2)
y93T7 dison 'treet, north side looking south over clearing towards Monroe and
Gouverneur Streets.
P.L.Speer.
NO RDP OTUTTICN. September 18, 1939.
